HEADWORD: Slickens
<hw>Slick"ens</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Slick</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>The pulverized matter from
